    "steam_appid": 2283350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/4986caa4413957c53caaf461fbd79432.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=99 /></span><br><i>Starting from today, My name is Dawn! Don’t I look cute in this?</i><br><br>Dawn recently found out she’s transgender, and she’s ready to embrace this side of herself to its fullest! In a world where humans coexist peacefully with vampires, demons, and other magical beings, she hopes to transform her body for the best.<br>Helped by Lucia, her asexual succubus friend, she soon finds herself in a tricky situation: her body has changed, yes, but she’s also a zombie now!<br><br>“Reborn a zombie!” is a queer story about friendship, acceptance, and a world full of cute monsters! Will she find happiness at the end of her journey, or is it the start of a new one?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/6cbde522c032cc859a80749768085620.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=99 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/7e091f5a010ec619720037db18feff5f.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=155 /></span><br>Our protagonist! She’s chipper, curious about anything magic, and wants to live in a body that is right for her! Her journey will lead her to Providence, the new capital of magiis.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/5b66178f6655411647e9ae3a8cd2e138.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=155 /></span><br>A succubus from the Demon Realm and talented spell weaver. Her asexuality often clashes with people’s expectation of a succubus, but she found relief in Dawn’s innocent friendship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/a39893afb2a392fb176c8778ce22e8c1.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=155 /></span><br>A powerful dragon who decided to help Dawn in this bizarre world, but a certain demon isn’t too keen on having her around…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283350/extras/a46db4b9a9761f3f0b272e7310472e48.avif?t=1758184414\" width=587 height=99 /></span><br>-17k words (about 2 hours of playtime)<br>-Backgrounds animated with visual effects for more magic!<br>-A queer story featuring a trans protagonist, a very cute ace succubus and a very buff dragon-lady!",
